'''talat-''' is a [[Quenya]] verb root meaning "to fall down".<ref>{{L|347}}</ref> 
==Etymology==
From a [[PQ]] [[root]] [[TALÁT]]<ref>{{LR|Etymologies}}</ref>
==Forms==
*''talanta'' (past participle) "fallen"<ref>{{LR|P1III2}}, p.72 (as ''talant'''ie''''' "he '''is''' fallen")</ref>
